EN: There are many fruit trees around the greenhouse, giving a fresh feeling.

ZH: 大棚的地面铺着黑色塑料膜，保持湿度。
EN: The floor of the greenhouse is covered with black plastic film to maintain humidity.

ZH: 大棚内设置了自动浇水系统，方便管理。
EN: An automatic watering system is installed in the greenhouse for easy management.

